Run \fB$ gcloud help\fR for details.



.SH "EXAMPLES"

To create a node group, run:

.RS 2m
$ gcloud alpha compute sole\-tenancy node\-groups create \e
    my\-node\-group \-\-node\-template=example\-template \-\-target\-size=4
.RE



